非法操縱妓女賣淫集團</strong><br />\n<br />\n鑒於近日有無辜香港市民慘遭黑勢力人仕襲擊，現懇切呼籲各香港市民不論男女，請慎防本地非法操縱妓女賣淫集團，保障自身安全，萬事小心，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">切忌助長黑惡勢力氣焰</span></strong>"},{"pid":"225c577e31711e44368bea26b201cb72d614c922","tid":1471248,"uid":238051,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T14:26:44.000Z","msg":"輕推9"},{"pid":"9e87f26d01ebc986f3a936a4455817ce514e7d57","tid":1471248,"uid":238051,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T18:56:14.000Z","msg":"推10"},{"pid":"64ed56a1377d1f55b1e8130409a3309fbed78961","tid":1471248,"uid":280547,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T19:00:43.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"14f58b88001067ea96e90bd7fb3bbb594d0c510f","tid":1471248,"uid":238051,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T02:59:52.000Z","msg":"認真討論冇人理<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f363fd0f02b799e196c69d4c13ca0d5dc94900ea","tid":1471248,"uid":173852,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T03:18:08.000Z","msg":"小弟既見解：<br />\n<br />\n1.討論要堂堂正正，唔好意氣用事，或者諗住呃人，搞小動作，岩就岩，錯就錯，唔好粉飾，認完錯就再黎過<br />\n(有野私下係telegram傾)<br />\n<br />\n2.上街既，大家講明軍規，違反就係鬼<br />\n(緊急時候另計，例如比警察追打時，但乜事都無你就黎掉磚燒野，咁係點玩法？)<br />\n<br />\n簡單講，即係要清楚D、簡明D，一含糊就有機會比人利用"},{"pid":"6ebed53faa441b7962ee23dac4a551d0bc280623","tid":1471248,"uid":67223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T03:30:34.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"52aca69d7cb389ae312eb4b4a27a09efdb7068df","tid":1471248,"uid":292980,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T06:29:33.000Z","msg":"可能間諜的用途係令你地互相猜疑，減慢決策時間，轉移焦點去捉鬼，再引起內鬥分列。而最後大家各自以個人單獨去抗爭。瓦解場運動"},{"pid":"eb8e4ff42bbb57d561de4468189646f8734777a9","tid":1471248,"uid":47268,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-11T20:04:07.000Z","msg":"想知樓主係咪比黑警捉撚咗<br />\n<br />\n無啦啦潛咗水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d9bc4f47fd577b9a9176aeb938de1c12b34c5b72","tid":1471248,"uid":2764,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"eb8e4ff42bbb57d561de4468189646f8734777a9","tid":1471248,"uid":47268,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-11T20:04:07.000Z","msg":"想知樓主係咪比黑警捉撚咗<br />\n<br />\n無啦啦潛咗水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-11T20:57:25.000Z","msg":"推呢個"}]}